TEXT(beginproblem());

$a=random(1,9,1); 
$b=random(1,9,1); 
$c=random(1,9,1); if ($a == $c) { $c++; }
$d=random(1,9,1); if ($d == $b) { $d++; }

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));

The slope of the line through the points \( ($a,$b) \) and 
\( ($c,$d) \) is  \{ ans_rule(20) \}.

EOT

$answer = ($d-$b)/($c-$a);

ANS(num_cmp($answer));

$a=random(1,9,1); 
$b=random(1,9,1); 
$c=random(1,9,1); if ($a == $c) { $c++; }
$d=random(1,9,1); if ($d == $b) { $d++; }

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));

The slope of the line through the points \( ($a,$b) \) and 
\( ($c,$d) \) is  \{ ans_rule(20) \}.

EOT

$answer = ($d-$b)/($c-$a);

ANS(num_cmp($answer));

